These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
House: cottage, wooden, tower, farmhouse
There 4 different types of food: radish, blueberry, orange, zucchini
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left or far right##3
4. the tower house is on the right of the person eating orange##1
5. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating orange##2
6. the farmhouse house is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| House   | farmhouse | cottage     | tower | wooden |
| Food     | radish     | orange | zucchini  | blueberry      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, horse, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, drawing, baking
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Pet   | cat | lizard    | turtle     | horse  |
| Hobby     | sudoku    | drawing | collecting | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, almond-milk, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | fanta   | almond-milk   | milk  | sprite |
| Transport           | taxi | quad-bike | boat | train  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, pineapple, cauliflower, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, techno, country
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating radish and the fan of techno##2
3. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
4. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | pineapple | radish | zucchini | cauliflower  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | metal   | country  | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, motorbike, taxi
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lilac, black, orange
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person who likes orange is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Transport   | van    | roller   | motorbike | taxi    |
| Color      | lilac | red | black       | orange |

