.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, japanese, british, chinese
4 different games are played: go, poker, backgammon, canasta
1. the chinese is on the right of the british##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing canasta and the british##2
3. the person playing go is between the person playing backgammon and the german##2
4. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the chinese##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Nationality    | german | british | chinese | japanese |
| Game   | poker | go  | backgammon    | canasta  |

