.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, animation, family
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, coral, grey, lilac
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching family movies##2
5. the person who likes coral is the person who likes coral##1
6. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes grey and the person watching family movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family | animation | drama     |
| Color     | blue | lilac  | coral   | grey |

