.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, rock, gospel
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, iced-tea, water
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking water is the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of dubstep is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | ambient | dubstep   | rock      | gospel      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | iced-tea | lemonade | water |

