.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, spy, sports, adventure
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, soy-milk, tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person watching sports movies is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | spy | sports      | adventure   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | coffee    | iced-tea | tea |

