.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
House: modern, wooden, craftsman, victorian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, march, december
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the modern house##3
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| House       | modern | craftsman | victorian    | wooden      |
| Birthday   | march       | december       | february | july |

