2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | animation  | epic | comedy |
| Birthday     | june | may | november     | september    |

