.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, alhambra, aristoff
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk  | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Cigar           | alhambra     | aristoff | bluemaster    | oliveros     |

