.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
City: berlin, hannover, edinburgh, nizza
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina, siglo, montecristo
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| City   | hannover  | berlin | nizza  | edinburgh      |
| Cigar    | montecristo | bluemaster | siglo | vegafina |

