.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, garlic, apricot, kale
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, bird, rabbit
1. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person eating garlic is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating apricot##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
6. the owner of the bird is the person eating lime##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Food         | garlic | kale | apricot | lime |
| Pet   | rabbit     | dog       | chinchilla   | bird      |

