2. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | rock | folk | funk |
| Pet         | dog  | hedgehog   | turtle | horse     |

