The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, nurse, chef, social-worker
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the nurse##3
4. the nurse is on the right of the mechanic##1
5. the chef is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| City      | london | hamburg    | boston  | paris |
| Job   | mechanic       | nurse | chef | social-worker  |

