3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
5. the havana-smoker is between the person drinking sprite and the davidoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Beverage   | 7up | iced-tea  | juice  | sprite |
| Cigar           | ritmeester    | davidoff | havana | swisher |

