.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, polish, brazilian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, drama, disaster, spy
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the italian##1
7. the polish is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | italian     | polish          | brazilian |
| Movie-Genre      | family | drama | spy | disaster  |

 